msgstr "Instalar AI Content Signals"

#: includes/class-tccl-promo-banner.php:88
msgid "Speed up your WordPress"
msgstr "Acelera tu WordPress"

#: includes/class-tccl-promo-banner.php:89
msgid "Comprehensive performance optimizations: critical CSS, lazy loading, cache rules, and 30+ tweaks with zero configuration."
msgstr "Optimizaciones integrales de rendimiento: CSS crítico, carga diferida, reglas de caché y más de 30 ajustes sin necesidad de configuración."

#: includes/class-tccl-promo-banner.php:90
msgid "Install Zero Config Performance"
msgstr "Instalar Zero Config Performance"

#: includes/class-tccl-promo-banner.php:94
msgid "Back to Classic Editor"
msgstr "Vuelve al editor clásico"

